cs.AI, cs.IOT, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the use of machine intelligence (MI) in the context of Internet of Things (IoT) and proposes a novel approach to distribute intelligence to the edge devices. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.IOT (Internet of Things) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the impact of this approach on the whole MI ecosystem, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
